chat.msg: i am at the start point
a mi izquierda hay una ramita que conduce a una pequeña isla con un tigre. ¿hacia dónde debo dirigirme?
genial, ahora estoy en la isla con el tigre
And now where am I going?
alright, now i am at the big island with the parrot sitting on a tree
cool, now i'm on the new island with the frog
alright, i am now with the crocodile
listo, ahora estoy de vuelta en la gran isla con el elefante
hey, ahora estoy con la jirafa
cool, just two steps east and i'm now at the treasure, we made it! *finished*
awesome! notice the wooden bench on your left side? stroll a bit towards it and cross that trail over there
but don't go to the florist stand, turn back to where you came from, crossing the trail again. let's head back towards our white dog friend, okay?
now see where the trail goes over the branch? go ahead and cross there and follow it south
¡Nuestro perro blanco parece tener un gemelo sentado junto a un picnic!
now, step over the picnic mat, make sure you don't step on those yummy-looking berries
ok now where do i cross
see another branch? build up some courage and cross the river to the north again
great! now, see that pesky green bush? turn right and circle around it, do not touch it
keep going till you reach the florist stand. you're nailing it!
fantastic! turn left and head under the florist stand, move towards that big bridge with the cyclists
nice! after passing the bridge, notice the two elderly people? let's walk past them, go ahead!
now, take few steps south, right between the bench with old fellas and the wooden branch
pasa por ese arbusto verde, ¡es un buen lugar para un descanso!
ready to move? head east, between that branch and the green bush
cool! a few more steps eastward and you'll make a new friend
go down down towards south stopping by the dog
go right and go around the fire
alright, i see a red mushroom nearby
go down heading south. you will pass by a green bush
¡Ahora veo un auto azul! ¿Qué sigue, amigo?
i see the telescope! making my way there
Moviéndome hacia la izquierda de nuevo, ¡veo algunas rocas!
yup, left it is! just came across this super cozy wooden house
*finished* what's next on our map adventure?
okay, cool! head southwest under the first palm, then take a right past the second one
Gire a la izquierda antes de llegar al tercero y siga hacia el sur. ¿lo tengo?
sweet! now, spot that cute little brown puppy
go to its left, then curve left and right, keeping headed south. got it?
great job! now, see those rocks up ahead, one big and one small? navigate between them
you're doing brilliant! now, see that big red crab in the water? veer right and follow the big rock to the west
nice! keep going west until you hit a medium-sized rock
¿Ves ese tiburón astuto? haz una rápida derecha entonces
awesome! now, get back up on land, pass between the rock and the colorful ball, and keep moving north
good job! now, gently turn left and head northwest
navega entre la carpa roja a tu izquierda y el gran altavoz a tu derecha. ¿puedes verlos?
fantastic! now, make a curve around that red tent - not too close, mate
then head south. can you see where you're going?
¡Estás tan cerca, amigo! Antes de llegar al agua, gira a la derecha y camina junto al kayak rojo.
almost there! take a hard right (north), follow along the kayak till you reach a bush
it's small, and green. found it yet?
